    },
    {
      "name": "Gloaming Wyrmscale Aura",
      "type": "feature",
      "system": {
        "keywords": [],
        "power": null,
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The dragon's scales create a 3 aura of dark supernatural fog around them that feeds on their victims' fears and provides concealment to the dragon only. Each enemy who starts their turn in the area takes [[/damage 2 psychic]] damage. Additionally, whenever one or more enemies is in the area, the dragon's abilities deal an extra [[/damage 3 psychic]] damage.</p>",
          "director": ""
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Shadow Skulk",
      "type": "feature",
      "system": {
        "keywords": [],
        "power": null,
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Once per turn, the dragon can shift up to their speed, leaving behind a 4 cube area of magical darkness in their starting space that lasts until the end of the encounter. The dragon ignores concealment created by this darkness. Any enemy who ends their turn in the area and has I &lt; 3 is frightened of the dragon until the end of their next turn.</p>",
          "director": ""
        }
      }
